content.body:
### Shop 265/65R17 Tire Size The 265/65R17 is a pretty common tire size on trucks, crossovers and SUVs; you’ll find it on the Ford Ranger, Chevrolet Colorado, Toyota Tacoma and older models of the GMC Suburban 1500, Toyota 4 Runner and Nissan XTerra. For most drivers of light trucks and crossovers, all-season tires make the most sense thanks to their compromise of ride quality, low noise, solid handling and year-round traction, even in light snow and slush. Some of our recommended premium all-season tires in the 265/65R17 size include the Michelin Defender LTX M/S, Continental TerrainContact H/T, Falken Wildpeak H/T02, and [Kumho Crugen HT51](https://simpletire.com/brands/kumho-tires/crugen-ht51). Popular vehicles: 2020-2021 Ford Ranger
2015-2021 Chevrolet Colorado
2005-2021 Toyota Tacoma
2000-2006 GMC Suburban 1500
2002-2009 Toyota 4Runner
2002-2015 Nissan XTerra Of course if you’re driving a light truck or SUV that’s equipped with 4WD, all-terrain tires are a great option too. All-terrain tires feature a more aggressive tread pattern and tougher casing design for confident grip off the pavement, while still delivering good road manners. Check out all terrain tires like the Toyo Open Country A/T III, BFGoodrich All-Terrain T/A KO2, [Yokohama Geolandar X-AT](https://simpletire.com/brands/yokohama-tires/geolandar-x-at), or Mickey Thompson Deegan 38 A/T. All-terrain tires are good at tackling everything, but sometimes they struggle in deep snow and slush. That’s when you need dedicated winter tires with their optimized tread pattern, network of sipes to boost traction and more-pliable tread formulation to stay flexible in cold weather. Premium winter tires in the 265/65R17 size would include the [Bridgestone Blizzak DM-V2](https://simpletire.com/brands/bridgestone-tires/blizzak-dm-v2), Nokian Hakkapeliitta 9 SUV, General Grabber Arctic, and Firestone Winterforce 2 UV. Whether you drive a Chevrolet Colorado, Ford Ranger, Toyota Tacoma, or something else, SimpleTire has a set of 265/65R17 tires that meets your needs at a great price!
